==Student Counselling==
LearnHub had an office in [[Gurgaon]], Haryana, India. LearnHub student counsellors guided students with respect to admissions, entrance exam prep, financial aid and visas for universities and colleges around the world.<ref>{{cite web| publisher=Hindustan Times| title=Mississippi State University awards $190,800 worth scholarships to LearnHub candidates from India| url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Mississippi-State-University-awards-190-800-worth-scholarships-to-LearnHub-candidates-from-India/Article1-578282.aspx| date=July 27, 2010| accessdate=August 4, 2010}}</ref>
